			Postal
			An IMAP mail check applet for the ROX panel.
			by Ken Hayber

Brief
~~~~~
Other Mail applets for ROX only check local mailboxes (e.g. /var/mail/username).

I wanted one to check my IMAP folders, so this is it.  See the TODO file for 
possible future additions.

